==Mandarin==

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: qiān lĭ yīn yuán yī xiàn qiān

===Idiom===
'''[[千]][[里]][[姻缘]][[一线]][[牵]]'''

# True love will remain, despite separation of great distances, even if by only a single thread.

===Alternate forms===
[[千里姻緣一線牽]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

